# CSS and UI Styling Patterns

## Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary**: Blue (`bg-blue-600`, `text-blue-600`, `border-blue-500`)
- **Success**: Green (`bg-green-600`, `text-green-600`)  
- **Error**: Red (`bg-red-600`, `text-red-600`)
- **Gray Scale**: `gray-50` to `gray-900` for backgrounds and text
- **Dark Mode**: Always provide dark variants

### Typography
- **Headers**: `text-xl font-semibold` or `text-2xl font-bold`
- **Code**: `font-mono` with `bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700` background
- **Small text**: `text-sm` for labels and secondary information

## Component Styling Patterns

### Cards and Containers
```html
<div className="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
  <!-- Card content -->
</div>
```

### Buttons
```html
<!-- Primary Button -->
<button className="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
  Button Text
</button>

<!-- Secondary Button -->  
<button className="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
  Secondary
</button>
```

### Form Elements
```html
<!-- Input Field -->
<input 
  className="flex-grow p-2 border rounded-md dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
  type="text"
/>

<!-- Select Dropdown -->
<select className="p-2 border rounded-md dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
  <option>Option</option>
</select>
```

## Dark Mode Support

### Implementation Pattern
- Always provide dark mode variants for all interactive elements
- Use `dark:` prefix for dark mode styles
- **Backgrounds**: `bg-white dark:bg-gray-800` for main containers
- **Text**: `text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100` for primary text  
- **Borders**: `border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600`

### Color Mapping
- Light backgrounds → `gray-800`, `gray-900` in dark mode
- Dark text → `gray-100`, `gray-200` in dark mode  
- Light borders → `gray-600`, `gray-700` in dark mode

## Responsive Design

### Breakpoint Usage
- **Mobile First**: Base styles for mobile, use `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` for larger screens
- **Layout**: `flex flex-col lg:flex-row` for responsive layouts
- **Text**: `text-center lg:text-left` for responsive alignment
- **Spacing**: `p-6 sm:p-12 md:p-24` for responsive padding

### Grid and Flex Patterns
```html
<!-- Responsive Grid -->
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
  <!-- Grid items -->
</div>

<!-- Responsive Flex -->
<div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-between">
  <!-- Flex items -->
</div>
```

## State-Based Styling

### Loading States
```html
<button disabled={isLoading} className="... disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">
  {isLoading ? 'Loading...' : 'Action'}
</button>
```

### Error States
```html
<div className="bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900 border border-red-400 text-red-700 dark:text-red-200 px-4 py-3 rounded">
  <strong className="font-bold">Error:</strong>
  <span className="block sm:inline"> {errorMessage}</span>
</div>
```

### Success States  
```html
<p className="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-sm">
  Operation completed successfully!
</p>
```

## Animation and Transitions

### Standard Transitions
- **Buttons**: `transition duration-150 ease-in-out`
- **Color Changes**: `transition-colors duration-200`
- **Layout Changes**: `transition-all duration-300`

### Hover Effects
- **Buttons**: `hover:bg-blue-700` (darken primary color)
- **Cards**: `hover:shadow-lg` (increase shadow)
- **Links**: `hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300`

## Layout Patterns

### Main Container
```html
<main className="flex min-h-screen flex-col items-center justify-start p-6 sm:p-12 md:p-24 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div className="w-full max-w-5xl">
    <!-- Content -->
  </div>
</main>
```

### Section Spacing
- Use `space-y-8` for vertical spacing between sections
- Use `mb-6` or `mb-8` for consistent bottom margins
- Use `gap-4` or `gap-6` for flex/grid spacing
